      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all restoration enthusiasts and weekend mechanics! This vehicle is the ultimate project car, offering a fantastic opportunity for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a classic back to life. While it currently requires comprehensive mechanical and cosmetic attention, it serves as a solid foundation with plenty of potential for the right owner. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
