    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and the upholstery is well-preserved, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a documented service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. You can expect a car that looks great and performs reliably without needing immediate repairs.",
