    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. It remains in a pristine, showroom-quality state, exhibiting no discernible wear and maintaining its original factory luster. Meticulously maintained and mechanically flawless, this unit offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate this unblemished example of engineering excellence.",
